queries.sql: SELECT `jt`.`id`, `jt`.`ecpcode` AS `ecpcode`, `e`.`customer_name`, `jt`.`trackingId` AS `trackingId`, GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT CONCAT( "<span class=\"badge fs-6 mb-3\" style='color: ", `tb`.`text_color`, "; background-color: ", `tb`.`background_color`, ";'>", `tb`.`tag_name`, "</span>" ) SEPARATOR " " ) AS tagsBeta, GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT CONCAT( "<span class=\"badge fs-6 mb-3\" style='color: ", `tj`.`text_color`, "; background-color: ", `tj`.`background_color`, ";'>", `tj`.`tag_name`, "</span>" ) SEPARATOR " " ) AS tagsJob, GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT CONCAT( aimg.ass_imgg ) ) AS image, `ct`.`categoriesName`, DATE_FORMAT(jt.createdate, "%d/%m/%Y %H:%i") AS createdate, `js`.`statusname`, `e`.`morning_only`, `e`.`evening_only`, `e`.`working_day_only`, `e`.`customer_type`, `jt`.`calljob`, `jt`.`capture`, `categoriesName`, `e`.`customer_alert_1`, `jt`.`jobStatus`, `oc`.`cyclename`, `jt`.`orderCycleId` as `ocid`, `jt`.`shipto`, `jt`.`totalOrder`, DATE_FORMAT(jt.createdate, "%Y-%m-%d") AS createdatenoformat, `us`.`user_name` as `calluser`, `jt`.`createuser` FROM `jobtask` `jt` JOIN `ecp` `e` ON `jt`.`ecpid` = `e`.`id` LEFT JOIN `tagsbeta` `tbeta` ON `jt`.`id` = `tbeta`.`jobid` LEFT JOIN `tagsjob` `tjob` ON `jt`.`id` = `tjob`.`jobid` LEFT JOIN `ass_img` `aimg` ON `jt`.`id` = `aimg`.`ass_code` LEFT JOIN `tags` `tb` ON `tbeta`.`tagsid` = `tb`.`id` LEFT JOIN `tags` `tj` ON `tjob`.`tagsid` = `tj`.`id` LEFT JOIN `tagscategory` `tc` ON `jt`.`tagsCategoryId` = `tc`.`id` LEFT JOIN `categories` `ct` ON `jt`.`categoryId` = `ct`.`id` LEFT JOIN `jobstatus` `js` ON `jt`.`jobStatus` = `js`.`id` LEFT JOIN `ordercycle` `oc` ON `jt`.`orderCycleId` = `oc`.`id` LEFT JOIN `users` `us` ON `jt`.`calluser` = `us`.`id` WHERE jt.trackingId IS NULL AND `jt`.`calljob` = 'Y' AND `jt`.`jobstatus` = 2 AND (`tc`.`isStock` IS NULL OR `tc`.`isStock` = "") AND `jt`.`calluser` = '3' GROUP BY `jt`.`id` ORDER BY `jt`.`createdate` ASC LIMIT 3
